reviews.review_text:
Great Audience Recording! The folks at MOTB have their SH!T together! This is an excellent audience recording, and made with only one microphone. Simply amazing! Do yourself a favor and click on the MOTB link that shows all the MOTB offerings on the Archive. Check out these shows:
7-2-89 FOB masterpiece
4-9-89 FOB wide stereo
8-6-71 Bertrando masterpiece (not MOTB)

Grate AUD Just a clean recording made even better. The boys are laid back, TC was always a great addition. Listen to the Airplane snippet prior to Dark Star, never can get enough Pig neither, for perfectionist, humble yourselves and dismiss the cuts before the tunes, a lot of tapers waited till the song started to save tape. That pause button always has the feel of the AUD recordings!!
Dark Star This DS has some of the "Feelin' Groovy" elements of 11-02. Not quite as developed as that night, however. Pretty interesting, nonetheless.
I wrote the backstory of this recording. https://www.facebook.com/sean.brady.94/posts/10209872553666551?pnref=story
